data.description: Welcome to the wonderful neighborhood of Fleetwood Park where this well-maintained, clean and bright 4 bedroom home awaits! Open main living area with gas fireplace leads out to the beautiful deck and large manicured backyard that truly stuns, especially when in bloom. Perfect as is or room to add a pool! Lower level offers a den and en-suite bedroom with laundry. Upper level with 3 more bedrooms and full bath. This is a well-loved home ready for its new owners to enjoy! Very close to NJ Transit train and bus for easy commute.
